{
  "texts": [
    "To obtain sufficient artifactual mutations, we added the same volume of nuclease-free water instead of the enzyme in the step.",
    "Exome was captured and libraries were prepared using the SureSelect V5 enrichment capture kit (Agilent).",
    "The libraries for targeted sequencing were prepared using our customized cancer panel (gene number of 359; panel size of 1.66 Mb) produced by Agilent in accordance with the manufacturer's instructions.",
    "The libraries were sequenced using the NovaSeq 6000 system (Illumina).",
    "To characterize the mutational signatures of breast cancers, we used Mutalisk, a web-based somatic mutation analysis toolkit with default options 37."
  ]
}